We are accepting a few more people for the month of july, we accept all skill levels from never traded before to trading for years! **This program includes:**

- Teaching you the ins and outs of screeners

- Access to all my live training classes for free as well as the recordings. 

**For those of you unfamiliar with my trading style and gains, heres my trade tracker** 
https://tinyurl.com/moneybagstradetracker 


**Day Trading Class 3 Starting Soon**

-Technical Indicator Types

In the end our goal was to reach 1000% gains by end of month and we closed it off at 1131%! Even though this month was slow in the market we still pulled off some crazy numbers! we also boosted our win loss with this new strategy!

**If you guys are interested in learning how to day trade either on your own or by following calls please send me a PM**
